			<div class="content" id="post-content-4548879">
									

<p>This theme was created utilizing a bunch of code from <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/component:black-highlighter-theme-dev">Black Highlighter</a> and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/component:old-money-theme">the Old Money Theme</a>, so this would not be possible by all the work put into those by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584287925" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;">Woedenaz</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584287925" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584287925" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, and whoever else had a hand in creating BHL.</p>
<p>The images used for this were sourced as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li>La Rue Sigil, La Rue scrawl, and the barely visible wood.png texture are images created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584287925" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span> and are licensed CC BY-SA 3.0</li>
<li>The fonts used are Parisienne, Rubik, and Courier Prime: <a href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Courier+Prime|Parisienne|Rubik&amp;display=swap">https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Courier+Prime|Parisienne|Rubik&amp;display=swap</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.deviantart.com/ftourini/art/tileable-wood-texture-214277777">The wood texture for the background</a></li>
</ul>

